<br />
<h2 class="text-center">Upgrade to Premium Membership</h2>
<br />
<p class="lead">With a premium membership, you will now have the ability to create private wikis.  Then, you can choose the collaborators who will have the ability to edit those wikis.  To get started, click on the button below!</p> 
<br />
<%= form_tag charges_path do %>
  <article>
    <label class="amount">
      <span>Amount: $15.00</span>
    </label>
  </article>

  <script src="https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js" class="stripe-button" data-key="<%= @stripe_btn_data[:key] %>" data-amount=<%= @stripe_btn_data[:amount] %> data-description="<%= @stripe_btn_data[:description] %>" ></script>
<% end %>